DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and pharmacokinetic characteristics of HD203 liquid with those of etanercept (enbrel) prefilled injection after subcutaneous injection
DOC.brief_title: Safety and Pharmacokinetic Characteristics of HD203 Liquid in Healthy Male Volunteers
DOC.criteria: 20 to 40 years of healthy volunteers Subject who had been treated with Etanercept before
